  "instructions": [
    "Heat the ghee or oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, turmeric, salt, and pepper, and stir for 1 minute.",
    "Add the rice and stir to coat the rice with the spice mixture.",
    "Add the water and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low, cover, and simmer for 18 minutes.",
    "Turn off the heat and let it sit for 5 minutes.",
    "Fluff the rice with a fork and serve hot."
